metadata.name: 4D Alien V1 by Romelus.3
metadata.description: The year is 2022. AI systems have just arrived in the hands of the general public. An idea on extraterrestrial life brought to life using the collective hive mind, rendered with AI and animated using a particle field, cooked on the GPU, this NFT is designed to bring the imagination of many, to what is possible today, and beyond.
